{"tid":1071164,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"好後悔去食百里香","createTime":"2019-03-21T07:02:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T11:10:52.000Z","uid":104804,"like":57,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"654389a086c9a36bbfb4c0950e1e437cda0399ce","tid":1071164,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:02:50.000Z","msg":"小弟本身好鍾意食牛脷<br />\n咁見到印度佬個post就心郁郁走過去試<br />\n50蚊有片蒜蓉多 白湯 凍飲 加碟飯都幾抵食咁<br />\n但問題個飯份量好細 蕃茄汁咸到仆街<br />\n牛脷就唔錯幾鬆軟<br />\n如果係公司樓下可以再試下既<br />\n專登走過去不了<br />\n利伸：我認係西客盡情屌我"},{"pid":"224b0e02ad30c2b6c94d0c3ef6658f35dbeca6fa","tid":1071164,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:04:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8bcf969a68d1c8b329fd66cb33a46b5bffa07be2","tid":1071164,"uid":38548,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:06:14.000Z","msg":"跟風野係咁架啦<br />\n<br />\n女就跟新假期<br />\n仔就跟連登"},{"pid":"8543e78d244d2e7bc86c19379d1c956adf0058ff","tid":1071164,"uid":1187,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:07:21.000Z","msg":"打手都信 自己攞嚟"},{"pid":"f9c128ce2e75bd4d7dab0c4cfd31bdfc5d4e6bb0","tid":1071164,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":34,"score":-34,"quote":{"pid":"224b0e02ad30c2b6c94d0c3ef6658f35dbeca6fa","tid":1071164,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:04:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:07:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5302aa0fd40cda400fee3fb891751bc948eaf75c","tid":1071164,"uid":31841,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:17:19.000Z","msg":"白痴仔先去食<br />\n個名改到勁長,其實普通茶仔野<br />\n仲要俾個狗兜你,當你係狗"},{"pid":"642a33968a8e4ca0cddc76e3d66ed3a417d9035b","tid":1071164,"uid":33359,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:17:45.000Z","msg":"又有傻仔中計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2638e9b3b843a81c513ab15b2c20d0a3f9658e3","tid":1071164,"uid":219337,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:18:20.000Z","msg":"成碟狗糧咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b91cf81006d546e4368735945eb7707e261c37ba","tid":1071164,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5302aa0fd40cda400fee3fb891751bc948eaf75c","tid":1071164,"uid":31841,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:17:19.000Z","msg":"白痴仔先去食<br />\n個名改到勁長,其實普通茶仔野<br />\n仲要俾個狗兜你,當你係狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:20:04.000Z","msg":"叉飯就叉飯啦，黯咩然銷咩魂飯呀"},{"pid":"e4d99efdcd1cd45ec76806e4da3290fbcf362f16","tid":1071164,"uid":242090,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:22:42.000Z","msg":"經過食過一次，真係幾旺場<br />\n燒雞幾抵食，熱辣辣，味道正常<br />\n$45 有湯 包 燒雞 薯角 飲品<br />\n我個日送埋焦糖布甸<br />\n我覺得可以取消湯同包，唔好食"},{"pid":"8cc3468197099f1c2d58f3837a263cd7e9cbcda6","tid":1071164,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:34:04.000Z","msg":"專登去食就真係不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n百里香只係性價比抵<br />\n多款式 啱打工仔/街坊食"},{"pid":"1a4aa958a6859df8408795608975b518df5fe8fc","tid":1071164,"uid":56701,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T08:00:46.000Z","msg":"其實佢係好貴...但份量真係唔夠真男人食...要食就一定要加雞翼...一定係食水牛城...<br />\n咁加埋75蚊.....其實抵過去真係西餐廳食...就咁同自己講抵食左...個心舒服啲!<br />\n<br />\n下次見到啲好似幾正既MENU,再諗吓一個人等咁Q耐又要死逼爛逼,附近一堆似我咁既獨撚或一堆印度人或一堆OFFICE友...再諗諗吓...我都係食返下層算啦...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b303d062aa11079172203fe4a0d9ca40fa05584e","tid":1071164,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T08:01:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實佢<span style=\"color: red;\">唔</span>係話好貴(起碼包湯嘢飲)...但份量真係唔夠真男人食...要食就一定要加雞翼...一定係食水牛城...<br />\n咁加埋75蚊.....其實抵過去真係西餐廳食...就咁同自己講抵食左...個心舒服啲!<br />\n<br />\n下次見到啲好似幾正既MENU,再諗吓一個人等咁Q耐又要死逼爛逼,附近一堆似我咁既獨撚或一堆印度人或一堆OFFICE友...再諗諗吓...我都係食返下層算啦...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6c34a115ffde6bc56b5cd174523828c5e6922f68","tid":1071164,"uid":170383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"642a33968a8e4ca0cddc76e3d66ed3a417d9035b","tid":1071164,"uid":33359,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:17:45.000Z","msg":"又有傻仔中計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T08:03:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f1ce9cab9c81ea07b2e966fdba47d4084846c32","tid":1071164,"uid":197337,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T08:03:51.000Z","msg":"打倒百里香霸權,還熟食中心晴空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a4d83c0e44d8e856e30657629bb231a75b150d","tid":1071164,"uid":29929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T08:32:14.000Z","msg":"印度狗話可以加多飯<br />\n你唔叫多飯個人問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"630271dee339b4d455104ed156511c69b7b03ce8","tid":1071164,"uid":27675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T08:33:16.000Z","msg":"不嬲都話間垃圾嘢餵狗都唔飽"},{"pid":"5f0641147fe253b2027cf95eeaf97102098a544b","tid":1071164,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"30a4d83c0e44d8e856e30657629bb231a75b150d","tid":1071164,"uid":29929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T08:32:14.000Z","msg":"印度狗話可以加多飯<br />\n你唔叫多飯個人問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T08:44:52.000Z","msg":"第一次去咩都唔識仲好驚<br />\n當然係我個人問題啦"},{"pid":"b0c83f8401d1df9b85e517bc82aa20950a05f0c6","tid":1071164,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b303d062aa11079172203fe4a0d9ca40fa05584e","t